# Enhanced Carrom Board — Resume Project

This is a polished, resume-ready browser Carrom game built with:
- HTML5 Canvas
- Vanilla JavaScript (ES6)
- CSS3

Key features:
- Realistic physics with mass-based collision resolution
- Pocket detection and queen scoring (+5)
- Local multiplayer (2 players) and single-player AI
- Touch & mouse input, power meter, configurable friction
- High-score persistence (localStorage), responsive layout
- Ready to host on GitHub Pages

## Run locally
1. Place the 4 files in a folder.
2. Open `index.html` in a modern browser.
3. Start from the menu. Drag the striker and release to shoot.

